'''乔伊·巴顿'''（{{lang-en|'''Joseph "Joey" Anthony Barton'''}}，簡稱'''Joey Barton'''，{{bd|1982年|9月2日|catidx=Barton, Joey}}），[[英格蘭|英格蘭]][[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，司職[[中場|中場]]，出身[[曼彻斯特城足球俱乐部|曼城]]青訓系統，其後轉投[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|纽卡斯尔联]]。

== 球會 ==
=== 曼城 ===
[[File:Barton_leap.jpg|thumb]] 
祖爾·巴頓的父親是一名蓋屋頂工人，亦是效力[[諾夫維治維多利亞足球會|-{zh-hans:诺斯维奇; zh-hk:諾夫維治; zh-tw:諾斯維奇;}-維多利亞]]（Northwich Victoria）的半職業球員，祖爾·巴頓參加[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]的青訓系統，但在14歲時遭放棄。在投考[[诺丁汉森林足球俱乐部|諾定咸森林]]因體型細小而被拒，最終獲[[曼城足球俱乐部|曼城]]賞識，提供學徒合約（Youth Training Scheme），先後為曼城的U-17、U-19及預備隊作賽。

祖爾·巴頓獲提升到由[[凯文·基冈|奇雲·基瑾]]任教的一隊，他當時擔任防守中場，在2003年4月5日首次替曼城一隊上陣，出戰[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|保頓]]，表現不錯，4月18日對[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|熱刺]]時取得首個入球<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/2936441.stm |title=City cruise past Spurs |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2020-09-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200904000517/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/2936441.stm }}</ref></small>，更在對[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]一役成為最佳球員，獲曼城提供一年合約<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/2950239.stm |title=Barton earns new deal |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2020-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200517111807/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/2950239.stm }}</ref></small>。2003年9月祖爾·巴頓續約兩年<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/3093518.stm |title=Barton agrees new deal |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2019-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190914121415/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/3093518.stm }}</ref></small>。之後一直也是擔任曼城的正選中場，他防守的能力非常好，而進攻的能力也不俗，常能為球隊取得入球。2004年5月[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]表示對土生土長的祖爾·巴頓有興趣<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/liverpool/3707795.stm |title=Liverpool eye duo |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2019-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190915130929/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/l/liverpool/3707795.stm }}</ref></small>，但祖爾·巴頓表示願意留隊<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/3551872.stm |title=Barton happy at Man City |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2019-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190909073351/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/3551872.stm }}</ref></small>，於9月續約三年<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/3679346.stm |title=Barton signs new City deal |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2020-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200517111807/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/3679346.stm }}</ref></small>。同年10月因膝傷動手術而需缺陣6星期<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/3737196.stm |title=Barton blow for Manchester City |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2019-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190911080419/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/3737196.stm }}</ref></small>。2006年初在談判續約條件時，祖爾·巴頓提出轉會要求被拒<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/4663950.stm |title=Man City reject request by Barton |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2019-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190910031204/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/4663950.stm }}</ref></small>，曼城同時拒絕[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米杜士堡]]的450萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]提價<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/4664768.stm |title=Man City reject Boro's Barton bid |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2021-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210609023644/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/4664768.stm }}</ref></small>。7月25日祖爾·巴頓終續約四年<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/5195524.stm |title=Barton & Richards sign new deals |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2021-02-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224214515/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/5195524.stm }}</ref></small>。

=== 紐卡素 ===
最終因為一連串的紀律問題，所以被曼城放棄<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/6633991.stm |title=Man City to decide Barton future |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2020-10-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201016230920/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/6633991.stm }}</ref></small>，在2007年夏天轉往[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|紐卡素]]，轉會費為580萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，簽約五年<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/6725067.stm |title=Barton completes move to Magpies |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2022-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220117142319/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/6725067.stm }}</ref></small>。7月23日在操練受傷，左腳第五蹠骨骨裂，需接受手術而缺陣6星期<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/6910550.stm |title=Injured Barton to undergo surgery |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2020-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200517111843/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/6910550.stm }}</ref></small>。

2008年7月29日，在祖爾·巴頓因襲擊及鬧事罪出獄後，紐卡素願意留用<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/7527503.stm |title=Magpies hand Barton second chance |access-date=2008-08-21 |archive-date=2021-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210303111445/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/7527503.stm }}</ref></small>。10月25日於停賽6場後在作客[[桑德兰足球俱乐部|新特蘭]]的「泰恩-威爾打吡」（Tyne Wear Derby）復出，下半場85分鐘後補入替，每次觸球也被主場球隊喝倒采<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7674086.stm |title=Sunderland 2-1 Newcastle |accessdate=2008-10-29 |archive-date=2015-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150704162644/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7674086.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，祖爾·巴頓在熱身時據報被敵對球迷用[[煙火|火箭]]襲擊<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7691715.stm |title=FA to assess Sunderland trouble |access-date=2008-10-29 |archive-date=2022-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220330071309/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7691715.stm }}</ref></small>。10月28日主場對[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|西布朗]]正選上陣，於10分鐘射入[[十二碼|十二碼]]協助球隊以2-1擊敗對手並使紐卡素脫離榜尾降級區域<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7683885.stm |title=Newcastle 2-1 West Brom |access-date=2008-10-29 |archive-date=2022-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220310101156/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7683885.stm }}</ref></small>。11月15日主場2-2賽和[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:维冈;zh-hk:韋根;zh-sg:威根;zh-tw:維根;}-]]，在上半場僅17分鐘即因[[李·卡特摩尔|-{zh-hans:卡特摩尔;zh-hk:卡達莫;zh-tw:卡特摩爾;}-]]的硬朗攔截而傷出<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7711309.stm |title=Newcastle 2-2 Wigan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-11-15 |accessdate=2009-05-04 |archive-date=2021-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210610052618/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/7711309.stm }}</ref></small>，賽後證實[[膝蓋|膝蓋]][[韌帶|韌帶]]受創而需缺陣兩個月<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/7733109.stm |title=Barton ruled out for two months |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2008-11-17 |accessdate=2009-05-04 }}</ref></small>。

[[File:Joey_Barton_corner.jpg|thumb]]
2009年5月3日作客0-3負於[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]，是祖爾·巴頓傷愈後首次正選出賽，下半場77分鐘祖爾·巴頓在右路[[角球|角球]]旗附近雙腳飛剷[[沙比·阿朗素|沙比·阿朗素]]，球證直接出示[[紅牌|紅牌]]將他驅逐離場<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8014847.stm |title=Liverpool 3-0 Newcastle |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-05-03 |accessdate=2009-05-04 |archive-date=2010-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101226184703/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8014847.stm }}</ref></small>，賽後領隊[[阿兰·希勒|舒利亞]]大表不滿並稱其行為愚蠢<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/8031815.stm |title=Barton 'stupidity' riles Shearer |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-05-03 |accessdate=2009-05-04 |archive-date=2022-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220503122553/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/8031815.stm }}</ref></small>。據報賽後祖爾·巴頓與舒利亞發生爭執<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/sport/football/article-1177334/Barton-suspended-following-swear-word-blast-Newcastle-bad-boy-Shearer-held-apart-dressing-room-bust-up.html?ITO=1490 |title=Barton suspended following swear-word blast as Newcastle bad boy and Shearer are held apart in dressing-room bust up |publisher=Mail Online |date=2009-05-05 |accessdate=2009-05-05 }}</ref></small>，5月5日紐卡素發表聲明：「祖爾·巴頓已被停止參賽直至另行通告。球會現時不作評論」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/8033495.stm |title=Barton hit by Magpies suspension |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-05-05 |accessdate=2009-05-05 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109025231/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/8033495.stm }}</ref></small>。

2009年7月9日祖爾·巴頓獲准在週六舉行對[[沙姆洛克流浪足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:沙姆洛克流浪; zh-hk:沙洛克流浪;  zh-tw: 沙姆洛克流浪者;}-]]的季前[[熱身賽|熱身賽]]歸隊<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/8143433.stm |title=Barton set for Magpies comeback |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-07-09 |accessdate=2009-07-10 |archive-date=2019-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913124054/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/8143433.stm }}</ref></small>。8月8日在紐卡素降班[[英冠|英冠]]首場比賽作客對[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|西布朗]]下半場獲派後補上陣<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8185944.stm |title=West Brom 1-1 Newcastle |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-08-08 |accessdate=2009-10-03 |archive-date=2020-11-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201122090754/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8185944.stm }}</ref></small>，一星期後主場3-0擊敗[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]更重獲正選席位<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8194911.stm |title=Newcastle 3-0 Reading |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-08-15 |accessdate=2009-10-03 |archive-date=2009-08-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090817164124/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8194911.stm }}</ref></small>。10月1日因傷缺席3場比賽後，祖爾·巴頓受傷的右腳進行探查手術，需要長期養傷<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/leagues/championship/newcastleunited/6253958/Newcastles-Joey-Barton-faces-months-out-after-foot-surgery.html |title=Newcastle's Joey Barton faces months out after foot surgery |publisher=telegraph.co.uk |date=2009-10-02 |accessdate=2009-10-03 |archive-date=2012-09-13 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120913104501/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/sport/football/leagues/championship/newcastleunited/6253958/Newcastles-Joey-Barton-faces-months-out-after-foot-surgery.html }}</ref></small>。在受傷前，本季由於[[奇雲·路蘭|-{zh-hans:凯文·诺兰;zh-hk:奇雲·路蘭;zh-tw:凱雲·諾蘭;}-]]及[[阿兰·史密斯|-{zh-hans:阿兰·史密斯;zh-hk:阿倫·史密夫;zh-tw:艾倫·史密斯;zh-mo:阿倫·史密夫;}-]]佔據中場中的席位，祖爾·巴頓移任右翼，他於2010年3月23日傷愈復出，於作客對[[唐卡斯特流浪足球俱乐部|唐卡士打]]下半場後補入替[[丹尼·格思里|-{zh-hans:格思里;zh-hk:古費爾;zh-tw:格思里;}-]]，並出席球季餘下的所有賽事，於4月3日作客3-2擊敗[[皮特堡联足球俱乐部|彼德堡]]時射入一記[[自由球|自由球]]，是他自2008年10月以來的首個入球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8594905.stm |title=Peterborough 2-3 Newcastle |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-04-03 |accessdate=2011-08-02 |archive-date=2010-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100406023646/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/8594905.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而紐卡素最終亦順利贏得聯賽冠軍而取得升班資格。

[[紐卡素2010年至2011年球季|2010/11年球季]]紐卡素重返[[英超|英超]]，祖爾·巴頓在唇上留了小鬍子，並稱在球隊取得首勝前不會剃掉<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/8920280.stm |title=Barton vows to keep his moustache until Newcastle win |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-08-17 |accessdate=2010-08-18 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109042728/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/8920280.stm }}</ref></small>，揭幕戰作客對[[曼徹斯特聯足球俱樂部|曼聯]]雖然以0-3敗陣而回，但次場回到主場卻淨勝到訪的[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]6-0，而祖爾·巴頓更為紐卡素先拔頭籌兼取得回歸英超後首球<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8926011.stm |title=Newcastle 6-0 Aston Villa |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-08-22 |accessdate=2011-08-02 |archive-date=2012-06-02 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/687zfLWDg?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8926011.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他整季表現出色，射入4球並交出9個助攻，協助球隊取得第12位及保留英超席位。但於2010年11月10日主場1-2不敵[[布莱克本流浪者足球俱乐部|布力般流浪]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/9163057.stm |title=Newcastle 1-2 Blackburn |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-11-10 |accessdate=2011-08-02 |archive-date=2021-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210412141213/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/9163057.stm }}</ref>，賽事中祖爾·巴頓拳擊[[摩頓·柏達臣|-{zh-hans:莫滕·佩德森;zh-hk:摩頓·柏達臣;zh-tw:莫滕·佩德森;}-]]，但[[球證|球證]][[米高·鍾斯|米高·鍾斯]]（Michael "Mike" Jones）沒有看到事發經過而當場沒有被罰，賽後球證審查錄影片段<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/9178056.stm |title=Referee to review Joey Barton 'punch' on Pedersen |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-11-11 |accessdate=2011-08-02 |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309120501/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/9178056.stm }}</ref>，以粗暴行為遭[[英格蘭足球總會|英格蘭足球總會]]判處停賽3場，祖爾·巴頓認罪並向-{zh-hans:莫滕·佩德森;zh-hk:摩頓·柏達臣;zh-tw:莫滕·佩德森;}-致歉<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/9181426.stm |title=Banned Joey Barton 'sorry' for Pedersen punch |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-11-11 |accessdate=2011-08-02 |archive-date=2021-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309115604/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/9181426.stm }}</ref>；12月11日紐卡素主場3-1擊敗[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/9268294.stm |title=Newcastle 3-1 Liverpool |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2010-12-11 |accessdate=2011-08-02 |archive-date=2012-06-02 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/687zwtDt2?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/9268294.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，祖爾·巴頓被指稱[[費蘭度·托利斯|-{zh-hans:费尔南多·托雷斯;zh-hant:費爾南多·托雷斯;zh-tw:費南多·托雷斯;zh-hk:費蘭度·托利斯;zh-mo:費蘭度·托利斯;}-]]為[[同性戀|同性戀者]]並向對方作出淫穢手勢<ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://www.whoateallthepies.tv/liverpool/59099/did-joey-barton-call-fernando-torres-a-fking-poof-photo.html |title=Did Joey Barton Call Fernando Torres A F**king Poof? (Photo) |publisher=''whoateallthepies.tv'' |accessdate=2011-08-02 |archive-date=2021-06-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210617092755/https://www.whoateallthepies.tv/liverpool/59099/did-joey-barton-call-fernando-torres-a-fking-poof-photo.html }}</ref>。2011年2月5日主場對[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿仙奴]]進行驚天大逆轉，半場落後0-4追平4-4完場，祖爾·巴頓射入兩個[[十二碼|十二碼]]，而其中他惹怒[[阿布·迪亚比|-{zh-hans:阿布·迪亚比;zh-hk:阿布·戴亞比;zh-tw:阿布·迪亞比;}-]]，導致對方被罰[[紅牌|紅牌]]離場正是賽事的轉捩點<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/9384154.stm |title=Newcastle 4-4 Arsenal |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-02-05 |accessdate=2011-08-02 |archive-date=2012-04-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120429181506/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/9384154.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2011年4月，尚餘一年合約的祖爾·巴頓在[[法國|法國]][[雜誌|雜誌]]「So Foot」表示自己是[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]最佳[[中場|中場]]球員，如紐卡素不能證實有爭標的野心，他將不會在新約上簽字<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/9451852.stm |title=Newcastle manager Pardew unfazed by Barton comments |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-04-08 |accessdate=2011-08-02 |archive-date=2019-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913134501/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/9451852.stm }}</ref>。5月25日他與紐卡素談判續約破裂<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13546072.stm |title=Joey Barton set for Newcastle United departure |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-05-25 |accessdate=2011-08-02 |archive-date=2011-10-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111028061015/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13546072.stm }}</ref>，並在[[Twitter|Twitter]]上留言表示自己雖然願意留隊，但紐卡素卻沒有提供新約<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13590926.stm |title=Joey Barton wants to remain at Newcastle |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-05-29 |accessdate=2011-08-02 |archive-date=2011-08-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110804190336/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/13590926.stm }}</ref>。續約談判拖拖拉拉，直到8月1日祖爾·巴頓再在Twitter上留言表示將於下午4時宣佈他的未來動向，但紐卡素先發制人，首先發出公告表示祖爾·巴頓可免費轉會離隊<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14366074.stm |title=Joey Barton allowed to leave Newcastle on free transfer |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-08-01 |accessdate=2011-08-02 |archive-date=2011-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111208023346/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14366074.stm }}</ref>，他遲了55分鐘才在Twitter上留言批評紐卡素董事會，表示以穿上黑白間條球衣為榮，並多謝「喜鵲」球迷一直的支持<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11678_7076222,00.html |title=Barton criticises Toon board |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2011-08-01 |accessdate=2011-08-02}}</ref>，而[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿仙奴]]、[[托特纳姆热刺足球俱乐部|熱刺]]及[[斯托克城足球俱乐部|史篤城]]隨即表示有意羅致<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_7076344,00.html |title=Trio tracking Barton |publisher=''Sky Sports'' |date=2011-08-01 |accessdate=2011-08-02 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310082842/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_7076344,00.html }}</ref>。但他仍有為球隊上陣多兩場聯賽，包括揭幕戰0-0賽和[[阿森纳足球俱乐部|阿仙奴]]，賽事中他認為對方新將[[热尔维尼奥|-{zh-hans:热尔维尼奥; zh-hk:謝雲奴;}-]]故意「插水」博取[[十二碼|十二碼]]，強行拉起對方引發混戰，後者因巴掌他而遭[[紅牌|紅牌]]驅逐離場，而他自己亦吃了一面[[黃牌|黃牌]]<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14519151.stm |title=Joey Barton 'not proud' of role in Gervinho spat |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-08-14 |accessdate=2011-08-29 |archive-date=2011-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111105110315/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14519151.stm }}</ref>。結果乔伊·巴顿被免費掛牌轉會。

=== 昆士柏流浪 ===
2011年8月26日祖爾·巴頓終免費轉投剛易主的[[英超|英超]]新軍[[女王公园巡游者足球俱乐部|昆士柏流浪]]，簽約四年<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14650167.stm |title=Joey Barton joins QPR from Newcastle United |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2011-08-26 |accessdate=2011-08-29 |archive-date=2012-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120123050243/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/14650167.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 國家隊 ==
2003年9月5日獲召首次代表[[英格蘭21歲以下足球代表隊|英格蘭U-21]]<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thefa.com/England/U21s/NewsAndFeatures/Postings/2003/09/64237.htm |title=Platt sings Barton's praise |accessdate=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2005-04-10 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20050410212050/http://www.thefa.com/England/U21s/NewsAndFeatures/Postings/2003/09/64237.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，在[[歐洲U-21足球錦標賽|歐洲U-21足球錦標賽]]外圍賽出戰馬其頓U-21，雙方1-1平手<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thefa.com/England/U21s/NewsAndFeatures/Postings/2003/09/64559.htm |title=U21s scuppered in Skopje |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2008-07-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080705172703/http://www.thefa.com/England/U21s/NewsAndFeatures/Postings/2003/09/64559.htm }}</ref></small>；四日後對葡萄牙U-21爭奪出線席位，祖爾·巴頓射入一球將比數扳平1-1，取得唯一的國際賽入球，但最後[[埃尔德·波斯蒂加|-{zh-hans:波斯蒂加;zh-hk:保斯迪加;zh-tw:波斯蒂加;}-]]一個涉嫌用手拍入的入球有效，作客的葡萄牙U-21以2-1獲勝，兼將英格蘭U-21淘汰出局<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/england/3091124.stm |title=England U21s crash out |accessdate=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2003-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030910100637/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/england/3091124.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

祖爾·巴頓於2007年2月2日首次獲選加入大國腳<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6319849.stm |title=Barton wins first England call-up |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2020-09-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200923012517/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6319849.stm }}</ref></small>，2月7日代表[[英格蘭足球代表隊|英格蘭足球代表隊]]在[[奧脫福球場|奧脫福球場]]友賽[[西班牙國家足球隊|西班牙]]<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thefa.com/England/SeniorTeam/NewsAndFeatures/Postings/2007/02/EnglandSpain1.htm |title=Spain take the spoils |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2008-07-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080709003237/http://www.thefa.com/England/SeniorTeam/NewsAndFeatures/Postings/2007/02/EnglandSpain1.htm }}</ref></small>，下半場78分鐘入替[[林柏特|林柏特]]，是唯一一次的大國腳出陣<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/6330177.stm |title=England 0-1 Spain |accessdate=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2012-03-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120312113017/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/internationals/6330177.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

== 紀律問題 ==
祖爾·巴頓自小在[[默西賽德郡|默西賽德郡]]的諾斯利（Knowsley）市區海頓（Huyton）成長，是四兄弟的長兄，父母在他14歲時離異，祖爾·巴頓隨父親及祖母居住，成功抗拒當地的[[毒品|毒品]]文化。

祖爾·巴頓的紀律問題一直讓人擔心及關注，2004年7月在對[[唐卡斯特流浪足球俱乐部|-{zh-hans:唐卡斯特;zh-hk:唐卡士打}-]]的季前熱身賽引發10人大爭執<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/3923995.stm |title=Keegan fury at Barton |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227035616/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/3923995.stm }}</ref></small>；同年12月他在[[聖誕|聖誕]][[派對|派對]]將[[雪茄|雪茄煙]]插向一個曼城的學徒球員杰米·坦迪（Jamie Tandy）的眼睛，因而被曼城罰扣6週薪金及考慮放棄<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/4116951.stm |title=Man City fine Barton for incident |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226230434/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/4116951.stm }}</ref></small>；杰米·坦迪於2008年8月15日民事控訴祖爾·巴頓損害其事業<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/7563196.stm |title=Barton faces action over assault |access-date=2008-08-21 |archive-date=2019-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190911064304/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/7563196.stm }}</ref></small>。

2005年5月4日在[[利物浦|利物浦]]市中心駕車意外撞傷一名正在祝捷的[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]球迷<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/merseyside/4517573.stm |title=Fan struck by football star's car |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2020-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200112133852/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/merseyside/4517573.stm }}</ref></small>；同年7月，他代表曼城參加在[[泰國|泰國]]舉行的季前熱身賽時，襲擊一名[[愛華頓|愛華頓]]球迷，先被遺返<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/4706625.stm |title=City to decide on Barton's future |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2021-04-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430001811/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/4706625.stm }}</ref></small>，再被球隊罰款12萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/4722645.stm |title=Barton is fined over hotel fracas |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227065810/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/4722645.stm }}</ref></small>。7月29日祖爾·巴頓17歲的弟弟米高·巴頓（Michael Barton）與表兄保羅·泰萊（Paul Taylor）在海頓以冰斧斫殺黑人少年安東尼·獲加（Anthony Walker），同年11月30日被判罪名成立<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/merseyside/4477156.stm |title=Youth guilty of racist axe murder |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2021-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210609022234/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/merseyside/4477156.stm }}</ref></small>，分別入獄17年及23年<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/merseyside/4487208.stm |title=Cousins jailed for racist murder |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2021-04-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210426031527/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/merseyside/4487208.stm }}</ref></small>。2007年11月6日對[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|富咸]]時領得6場比賽中的第5面[[黃牌|黃牌]]，自動停賽一場<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/4413958.stm |title=Barton given one-match suspension |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2019-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190909034656/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/4413958.stm }}</ref></small>。

2006年9月30日作客愛華頓時，向對方球迷露出[[臀部|臀部]]<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/5373474.stm |title=Everton 1-1 Man City |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2020-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200112202533/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/5373474.stm }}</ref></small>，雖然警方沒有跟進<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/5395778.stm |title=Police take no action over Barton |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2020-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200112202851/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/5395778.stm }}</ref></small>，仍遭[[英格蘭足球總會|英格蘭足總]]指控行為不檢，判罰2,000英鎊，但不用停賽<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/5409082.stm |title=Barton gets fine but escapes ban |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2020-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112033944/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/5409082.stm }}</ref></small>。

2007年2月10日作客1-2負於[[朴茨茅斯足球俱乐部|樸茨茅夫]]，完半場前祖爾·巴頓踏傷為主隊首開紀錄的[[柏度·文迪斯|-{zh-hans:佩德罗·门德斯;zh-hk:柏度·文迪斯;zh-tw:佩德羅·門德斯;}-]]（Pedro Mendes）的腳跟，文迪斯因傷離場，而祖爾·巴頓僅被罰[[黃牌|黃牌]]<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/6327163.stm |title=Portsmouth 2-1 Man City |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2019-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190915144815/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/6327163.stm }}</ref></small>，下半場主場球迷不斷向祖爾·巴頓喝倒事采，有指祖爾·巴頓向球迷作不文手勢<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/6353431.stm |title=Man City give backing to Barton |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227080503/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/6353431.stm }}</ref></small>，賽後[[英格蘭足球總會|英格蘭足球總會]]亦決定不追究<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/portsmouth/6360125.stm |title=FA takes no action against Barton |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2019-09-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913075337/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/p/portsmouth/6360125.stm }}</ref></small>。3月13日警方證實祖爾·巴頓在[[利物浦|利物浦]]與一名[[的士|的士]]司機發爭執，涉嫌襲擊及毀壞被捕<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/manchester/6445203.stm |title=City star arrested over assault |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2021-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210620141530/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/manchester/6445203.stm }}</ref></small>，最終於2008年5月30日獲判無罪<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/7428263.stm |title=Barton cleared over taxi damage |access-date=2008-08-21 |archive-date=2019-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190915083354/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/7428263.stm }}</ref></small>。同年5月1日在卡靈頓（Carrington）的訓練場上襲擊隊友[[奥斯马尼·达博|達保]]（Ousmane Dabo），導致後者臉部多處受傷，曼城禁止祖爾·巴頓在球季餘下的比賽上陣<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/6612933.stm |title=Man City ban Barton after bust-up |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227105617/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/m/man_city/6612933.stm }}</ref></small>。5月16日警方拘捕祖爾·巴頓<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/manchester/6660503.stm |title=Barton is arrested over assault |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2012-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120123102943/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/manchester/6660503.stm }}</ref></small>。7月11日警方再次拘捕祖爾·巴頓<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/manchester/6292818.stm |title=Police extend Joey Barton's bail |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2020-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200517111831/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/manchester/6292818.stm }}</ref></small>。8月2日被正式撿控傷人罪<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/manchester/6927605.stm |title=Barton faces player attack charge |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2021-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227071223/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/manchester/6927605.stm }}</ref></small>。8月9日祖爾·巴頓否認控罪<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/manchester/6938414.stm |title=Barton denies team-mate assault |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2021-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210510020526/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/manchester/6938414.stm }}</ref></small>。由於方便證人作供，審訊延期到球季結束後重開，期間前隊友[[西尔万·迪斯丁|-{zh-hans:西尔万·迪斯坦;zh-hk:西爾萬·迪斯坦;zh-tw:蕭凡·迪斯坦;}-]]（Sylvain Distin）因渡假缺席而被法庭判罰2,000[[英鎊|英鎊]]<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/manchester/7505721.stm |title=Distin fined for trial 'no-show' |access-date=2008-08-21 |archive-date=2019-09-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190915191118/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/manchester/7505721.stm }}</ref></small>，2008年6月30日，祖爾·巴頓承認控罪<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/7481822.stm |title=Barton admits team-mate assault |access-date=2008-08-21 |archive-date=2021-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210620023403/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/7481822.stm }}</ref></small>，被判入獄4個月，[[緩刑|緩刑]]兩年<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/7482620.stm |title=Barton is sentenced for assault |access-date=2008-08-21 |archive-date=2022-03-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220323002440/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/7482620.stm }}</ref></small>。英格蘭足總於2008年7月31日重提舊事，控訴祖爾·巴頓的暴力行為<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/7535664.stm |title=FA charges Barton over Dabo clash |access-date=2008-08-21 |archive-date=2021-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210609034407/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/7535664.stm }}</ref></small>，8月13日祖爾·巴頓承認指控<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/7559141.stm |title=Barton admits to violent conduct |access-date=2008-08-21 |archive-date=2021-03-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210301191246/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/7559141.stm }}</ref></small>，在2008年9月5日足總聆訊前祖爾·巴頓不會代表紐卡素上陣<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/7578184.stm |title=Barton sidelined until FA hearing |access-date=2008-08-28 |archive-date=2021-06-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210610011542/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/7578184.stm }}</ref></small>。9月5日，經過3小時聆訊，剛離任的紐卡素領隊[[凯文·基冈|凯文·基冈]]以[[傳真|傳真]]支持祖爾·巴頓，足總判罰停賽12場，6場即時執行而餘下6場暫緩，及罰款25,000[[英鎊|英鎊]]<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/7599647.stm |title=Banned Barton to miss six matches |access-date=2008-09-06 |archive-date=2019-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191104050133/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/7599647.stm }}</ref></small>。

2007年12月27日祖爾·巴頓再涉及另一宗傷人案而被捕<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/7162319.stm |title=Footballer Joey Barton arrested |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2019-09-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190911121027/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/7162319.stm }}</ref></small>，2008年1月3日才獲准保釋<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/7169108.stm |title=Footballer Barton freed on bail |access-date=2008-08-04 |archive-date=2021-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210423091427/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/7169108.stm }}</ref></small>。3月12日祖爾·巴頓上庭應訊，被控襲擊及鬧事，同案還有其弟安德魯（Andrew Barton）及表妹娜丁·威爾遜（Nadine Wilson），同獲准保釋直到4月23日再上庭<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/merseyside/7292072.stm |title=Footballer in court over assault |access-date=2008-08-21 |archive-date=2020-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200112005129/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/merseyside/7292072.stm }}</ref></small>。案情指祖爾·巴頓與家人於2007年[[节礼日|-{zh-hk:拆禮物日;zh-hans:节礼日;}-]]晚上到[[利物浦|利物浦]]市中心慶祝，期間祖爾·巴頓喝了大量[[淡啤酒|淡啤酒]]（lager），其後一行人到教堂街（Church Street）的[[麦当劳|麦当劳]]，與一班青年發生爭執後離開，途中再與其他人口角，這時祖爾·巴頓被[[閉路電視|閉路電視]]拍到將一名不辨身份男人推倒地上，先拳打對方4至5次，他的表妹向受害人拋擲食物，祖爾·巴頓再以拳打他15次；稍後祖爾·巴頓再襲擊一名16歲少年，導致對方[[牙齒|牙齒]]脫落。祖爾·巴頓表示極為後悔及承認受[[酒精|酒精]]影響，雖然[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|紐卡素]]領隊[[凯文·基冈|凯文·基冈]]出庭擔任品格證人，但仍於2008年5月20日被判入獄6個月，賠償牙齒脫落的少年2,500[[英鎊|英鎊]]，同案的安德魯及娜丁分別被判入獄4個月及6個月，但獲[[緩刑|緩刑]]兩年<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/7409943.stm |title=Joey Barton is jailed for assault |access-date=2008-08-21 |archive-date=2021-06-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210620011902/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/7409943.stm }}</ref></small>。7月28日，在服刑74日後獲釋出獄<small><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/manchester/7528581.stm |title=Joey Barton released from prison |access-date=2008-08-21 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109042425/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/uk_news/england/manchester/7528581.stm }}</ref></small>。

2009年季初有傳祖爾·巴頓在操練時與[[阿根廷|阿根廷]]隊友[[乔纳斯·古铁雷斯|-{zh-hans:乔纳斯·古铁雷斯; zh-hk:約拿斯·古迪利斯;}-]]及[[法布里西奥·科洛奇尼|-{zh-hans:法布里西奥·科洛奇尼; zh-hk:高路仙尼;}-]]發生爭執，其後更與看守領隊[[基斯·曉頓|基斯·曉頓]]（Chris Hughton）爭吵<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/8191579.stm |title=Hughton cools Barton row claims |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-08-09 |accessdate=2009-10-03 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226052748/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/8191579.stm }}</ref></small>。

2011年夏季[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|紐卡素]]前赴[[美國|美國]]進行季前[[熱身賽|熱身賽]]，但美國[[领事馆|领事馆]]拒絕發給祖爾·巴頓簽證，他只能跟隨預備隊到[[荷蘭|荷蘭]]集訓<ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-tyne-14134851 |title=Newcastle's Joey Barton denied US visa |publisher=[[BBC|''BBC News'']] |date=2011-07-13 |accessdate=2011-07-13 |archive-date=2020-11-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111175632/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-tyne-14134851 }}</ref>。

2012年英超煞科戰在與曼城一戰中因在球隊上蓄意傷人，所以他需要罰款7萬5千英鎊及受到12場禁賽令的處分。

